                <h1>Take of the week: Duke&#039;s hopes of an ACC Coastal title didn&#039;t perish in its loss to Virginia Tech </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/d9030a80-ea30-4fb3-bdc5-074f86e6c160.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;If&#x20;Daniel&#x20;Jones&#x20;can&#x20;play&#x20;like&#x20;he&#x20;did&#x20;before&#x20;his&#x20;injury,&#x20;Duke&#x20;still&#x20;has&#x20;a&#x20;chance&#x20;to&#x20;win&#x20;the&#x20;ACC&#x20;Coastal&#x20;Division.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>If Daniel Jones can play like he did before his injury, Duke still has a chance to win the ACC Coastal Division.</p>

